  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELL...HERE YOU ARE...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You wake up to silence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something is here. You can’t see it, but you can feel it. It watches. It waits. And it hunts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The base, once a haven on the moon's surface, is now a labyrinth of flickering lights, groaning metal, and half-seen horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/5d04d37c67076e5ac9eb593f8860ddf1.avif?t=1746616813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras_big/5d04d37c67076e5ac9eb593f8860ddf1.avif?t=1746616813 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corridor is a gamble, every corner hides the unknown. Your only tools are your instincts and what little you can scavenge along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you outwit the unseen predator? Can you escape the decaying moonbase before it collapses completely? Or will you be another silent victim of the creature lurking in the shadows?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Survival Horror:</strong> Every playthrough is different with a procedurally generated maze that keeps you on edge. No run is the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Atmosphere:</strong> 3D visuals with a retro-inspired dithering effect immerse you in a chilling, timeless aesthetic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person Tension:</strong> Limited visibility and environmental storytelling put you in the center of the fear. Every sound, every flicker of light, becomes a potential threat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test Your Nerves:</strong> It’s not just about finding your way out—it’s about staying alive long enough to escape.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.poster.avif?t=1746616813\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.webm?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.mp4?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.poster.avif?t=1746616813\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.webm?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.mp4?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELL...HERE YOU ARE...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You wake up to silence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something is here. You can’t see it, but you can feel it. It watches. It waits. And it hunts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The base, once a haven on the moon's surface, is now a labyrinth of flickering lights, groaning metal, and half-seen horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/5d04d37c67076e5ac9eb593f8860ddf1.avif?t=1746616813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras_big/5d04d37c67076e5ac9eb593f8860ddf1.avif?t=1746616813 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corridor is a gamble, every corner hides the unknown. Your only tools are your instincts and what little you can scavenge along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you outwit the unseen predator? Can you escape the decaying moonbase before it collapses completely? Or will you be another silent victim of the creature lurking in the shadows?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Survival Horror:</strong> Every playthrough is different with a procedurally generated maze that keeps you on edge. No run is the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Atmosphere:</strong> 3D visuals with a retro-inspired dithering effect immerse you in a chilling, timeless aesthetic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person Tension:</strong> Limited visibility and environmental storytelling put you in the center of the fear. Every sound, every flicker of light, becomes a potential threat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test Your Nerves:</strong> It’s not just about finding your way out—it’s about staying alive long enough to escape.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.poster.avif?t=1746616813\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.webm?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/276f29113366c759864723a2555a6a82.mp4?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.poster.avif?t=1746616813\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.webm?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636910/extras/dd52a717a8076850713318c9473b31c7.mp4?t=1746616813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
